4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals without prior knowledge, preparing them to become cybersecurity specialists. The program lasts 16 weeks and includes three live online classes per week, with a maximum class size of 16 students. Participants will learn essential skills in Windows, Linux, network and server administration, cloud security, and penetration testing. The bootcamp emphasizes risk management and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Upon completion, students receive an official certificate recognized by various institutions. Classes are available in both English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop